name: Inner-Foundation by LDSN
tagline: Inner-Foundation( IF ) is a foundation in the LDSN to make money for this team.
body:
### 欢迎访问IF (Inner-Foundation)
IF 作为一个内部基金，对内部一些可控制的收入进行再投资，以期待获取更多的运营资本，来支持社团的活动。
